      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，MarkAsProcessingCMD是从待处理到处理中。关于错误状态，这里有个特殊设计：处理中状态执行MarkOrderCompleteCMD时，可能会成功也可能失败——成功就到已完成，失败就进入错误状态。所以MarkOrderCompleteCMD有两个去向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "state_OrderProcessing",
        "MarkOrderCompleteCMD",
        "state_OrderCompleted",
